description: This file defines a custom exception class 'UserAlreadyRegisteredException' which extends a general exception class 'SimpleBankingGlobalException'. It is used to indicate that a user registration attempt failed because the user is already registered.

classes.name: UserAlreadyRegisteredException
classes.description: A specialized exception class indicating that a user has already been registered.

methods.name: UserAlreadyRegisteredException
methods.description: Constructor that initializes the exception with a message and a code.
